data.description:
Modern feel, granite kitchen counter tops, floating vanities. Stainless steel appliances with an open floor plan to living and dining. Large master bedroom with master suite and walk in closet. Privacy fence with decorative lighting. Beautifully turfed backyard for easy maintenance. Close proximity to main highways and shopping centers.

Tenant is responsible for all utilities (gas, water, and electric). Pets are welcome, damages to property are renters responsibility. 12 month lease required. First months rent and deposit due at signing. Tenant is responsible for general upkeep of the property.
